<OUTPUT_TEXT>
Understood. As a Bookkeeping Accounting And Auditing Clerk, I am prepared to perform various financial calculations including:

- Calculating amounts due from customers or to vendors
- Computing interest charges on loans or investments
- Determining account balances
- Calculating applicable discounts on purchases or sales
- Figuring equity positions in investments or businesses
- Computing principal amounts on loans or mortgages

I can assist with these calculations using appropriate formulas and accounting principles. Please provide the specific financial data and type of calculation needed, and I will perform the requested task.
</OUTPUT_TEXT>
